Properties.Caption: Просмотр регламентных отчетов
Properties.Tag: Select [K_BD].[CBD] As [Код бюджета], [K_TD].[CTD] As [Тип документа], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [K_PERIOD].[CPERIOD] As [Период], [DOC].[DU_O] As [Дата организации], [DOC].[DU_R] As [Дата утверждения распорядителя], [DOC].[DU] As [Дата утверждения], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL_PARENT] As [Распорядитель], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL] As [Организация] From ((((((([DOC] With (NoLock) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_PERIOD] With (NoLock) On (Mid([DOC].[CDOC],23,3)=[K_PERIOD].[CPERIOD])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Inner Join [K_BD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_BDID]=[K_BD].[K_BDID])) Left Join [DOC_DO] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[DOCID]=[DOC_DO].[DOCID])) Where [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[Apps_GroupsID]=GetApps_GroupsID() And |0 Group by [K_BD].[CBD], [K_TD].[CTD], [DOC].[CDOC], [K_PERIOD].[CPERIOD], [DOC].[DU_O], [DOC].[DU_R], [DOC].[DU], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL_PARENT], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр регламентных отчетов
